DATA CLOUD
Add Object Permissions to Custom Permission Sets for Data Cloud

Object permissions for new Data Cloud objects are added to all standard Data Cloud permission sets when the new objects is added. However, object permissions for new objects but must be manually added to custom permission sets. Use these object permissions to update any custom Data Cloud permission sets that were created before the new object was added to Data Cloud.
